10
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,080
Hello,

11
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:27,680
I'm Long Yunzhu from NAME.

12
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:29,180
(Long Yunzhu, member of NAME)

13
00:00:29,680 --> 00:00:30,080
Okay.

14
00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:30,600
Hi everyone.

15
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,200
I'm Ryan Zhao.

16
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,800
